Create Template

 

To start creating a template select Create template button from the Library page.

Fill following information in the Create template window:

  • The object  type for which you want to use the template
  • The name of the template
  • If the template will be primary
  • If the template will be used when creating an item or when uploading content in ConservationSpace

Press Ok button once you fill all necessary information.

A blank page opens where you can start to design your template. To save the template select Save button.
